sh stimulants or artificial additives. No significant side effects have been reported by users. However, individuals with pre-existing medical conditions, those on medication, or pregnant/nursing women should consult a healthcare professional before use."}}, {"@type": "Question", "name": "How long does Java Burn 2.0 take to work?", "acceptedAnswer": {"@type": "Answer", "text": "Most users report reduced daily fatigue within 2\u20133 weeks. More substantial benefits like increased energy, reduced cravings, and healthy weight management typically appear after 2\u20133 months of daily use. For best results, consistent use for 3\u20136 months is recommended."}}, {"@type": "Question", "name": "Where can I buy Java Burn 2.0?", "acceptedAnswer": {"@type": "Answer", "text": "Java Burn 2.0 is only available through its official website. It is not sold on Amazon, Walmart, or in retail stores. This ensures you receive the genuine product with full guarantee coverage. The official site offers 1-bottle, 3-bottle, and 6-bottle packages."}}, {"@type": "Question", "name": "Is Java Burn 2.0 worth the price?", "acceptedAnswer": {"@type": "Answer", "text": "At $49\u2013$79 per bottle (depending on the package), Java Burn 2.0 delivers 6 premium ingredients that would cost significantly more if purchased separately. The 6-bottle package at $49/bottle offers the best value. Coupled with the 60-day guarantee, it represents a low-risk investment in long-term metabolic health."}}]}];
